sjc.parser

Class StaticJavaV4BaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • sjc.parser.StaticJavaV4BaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StaticJavaV4Listener

    public class StaticJavaV4BaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements StaticJavaV4Listener
    This class provides an empty implementation of StaticJavaV4Listener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
